<p>Jazz Band meet on Thursdays from 7-9.30pm in the Music Room. We play a large variety of music, from swing classics to more modern tunes, and we&rsquo;re always open to suggestions!<br />Previous gigs include playing for the Durham University Swing Dance Society, the DSU Jazz Afternoon, Durham Street Food Project, our annual slot at the Durham Christmas markets, and plenty of concerts at college.<br />Open to anyone who plays wind, brass, drums, bass, keys or guitar, and of course vocals! No previous jazz experience required, and there is no membership fee.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>